data.name: Installer.Welcome.MainText
data.value:
Bloxstrap download karne ke liye shukriya.
Bloxstrap download karne ke liye sirf {0} aur {1} official websites hain, isliye kripya ensure karein ki aapne ise ek official source se download kiya ho.

data.name: Installer.Install.Location.Text
data.value: Roblox bhi is path par install hoga. Agar aap apne saare games ko alag drive par install karna chahte hain, to ise badal sakte hain. Agar nahi, to yeh waise ka waise rakhein, yeh recommend kiya jata hai.

data.name: Installer.Completion.Text
data.value:
Bloxstrap successfully install ho gaya hai.
Roblox abhi tak install nahi hua hai, yeh tab hoga jab aap pehli baar Bloxstrap ke saath ise launch karenge. Lekin, usse pehle, aap Bloxstrap ki settings configure karna chahein to kar sakte hain.
Saath hi, "Roblox Player" shortcut ka istemal karke Roblox ko launch karne se bachain, kyunki Bloxstrap ke saath Roblox launch nahi hoga. Agar aapko website se launch karte waqt Bloxstrap nahi dikhe, to bas ek baar desktop se Roblox ko Bloxstrap ke saath launch karke isse theek kar sakte hain.
Aap kya karna chahenge?

data.name: Uninstaller.Text
data.value:
Uninstall karne se Bloxstrap aapke system se remove ho jayega, aur agar default Roblox launcher abhi bhi installed hai toh use automatically reconfigure kar diya jayega.
Uninstall process ke baad kuch cheezein reh sakti hain, isliye aapko manually leftover files clean karni pad sakti hain jahan Bloxstrap install tha.
Bloxstrap "{1}" par install tha.

Jab yeh enabled hoga, to yeh automatically Settings band hone ke baad Roblox launch karega, aur Roblox band hone ke baad Settings dubara kholega. Yeh cycle tab tak chalega jab tak aap ise disable na karein.
Kya aap parikshan mode enable karna chahenge?

data.name: Bootstrapper.FilesInUse
data.value:
Bloxstrap ne Roblox ka adhunikaran karne ki koshish ki, lekin nahi kar pa raha hai kyunki Roblox ki faaylen abhi bhi upyog mein hain.
Kripya un anuprayogon ko band karein jo ho sakta hai ki Roblox ki faaylen ka upyog kar rahe hon, aur punah prarambh karein.
